{"tid":361472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】支那叔插隊反而叫我道歉","createTime":"2017-08-16T06:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T07:15:33.000Z","uid":128507,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2362ca5384fc7f8eb26a5da1bd667c93e05dc94","tid":361472,"uid":128507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T06:59:01.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人以為自己著得身光頸靚咁，係海洋公園排隊挽過山車企係我後面貼到勁埋，前胸貼後背，仲要開直播講野勁大聲，用鏡頭隊住其他人，不停問人佢靚唔靚仔，各位巴絲嚟答下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行慢小小就插隊，我拉番男朋友行前，忍左佢好耐，就撞左佢一下，踩到佢隻腳。係咁用粗口問候我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我講左句明明係你插隊先，淨係識話我對不起都無講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99你插隊我要講對唔住？？？？ ？<br />\n<br />\n就係呢條友啦，好想搵佢直播出嚟睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/145129_8063b52308f3c4e34d4cd6b1833cf4f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F145129_8063b52308f3c4e34d4cd6b1833cf4f0.jpg&h=9acf12e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1772bef870d4a8fea6546b685fd98285797e98a3","tid":361472,"uid":15355,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07:08:12.000Z","msg":"挽你老母臭閪呀"},{"pid":"9a77b320a94dc61b8f98d4562301c984c2198b61","tid":361472,"uid":99364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c4652e9b329d10c2c013eeb418ed929a6e64fd2","tid":361472,"uid":619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T07